== English ==
=== Adjective ===
'''crazy''' ('''crazier''', '''craziest''')
# [[insane]], [[demented]]
# out of control
#*When Jim gets on the motorcycle he goes '''crazy'''.
# overly excited or [[enthusiastic]]
# filled with foolish or unreasoned [[affection]]
